---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/Base.astro";

const meta = {
	description: "About LSY Blog",
	title: "About",
};
---

<PageLayout meta={meta}>
	<h1 class="title mb-6">About</h1>
	<div class="about-copy prose prose-sm prose-cactus max-w-none">
		<p>
			My name is Sung-Young (성영) Lee (이). "Sung" (晟) means bright, and "Young" (榮) means glory.
			"Lee" (李) is my family name.
		</p>
		<h2>Past</h2>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">Military Service at the United States Army Garrison (USAG) Humphreys.</strong></p>
		<p>Sergeant, 18 months service, 557th Military Police Company.</p>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">B.S. in EECS from Seoul National University (highest honors).</strong></p>
		<p>Research on mixed-signal ICs (e.g., PLL and ADC) (Advisor: Prof. Deog-Kyoon Jeong).</p>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">Ph.D. student at UT Austin (Advisor: Prof. David Z. Pan).</strong></p>
		<p>Research on transistor-level Electronics Design Automation (EDA).</p>
		<h2>Current</h2>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">Ph.D. student at UT Austin (Advisor: Prof. Keshav K. Pingali).</strong></p>
		<p>Research on Systems and Graph Analytics.</p>
		<h2 id="original-intro">Research Focus</h2>
		<p><strong class="text-accent">Efficient & Expressive ML</strong></p>
		<p>Specific short term interests are as follows:</p>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				Algorithm level
				<br />
				(1) Few-step generative models (e.g., one-step generation or distillation)
				<br />
				(2) Sample-efficient reinforcement learning (e.g., off-policy and offline)
			</li>
			<li>
				System level
				<br />
				(1) CUDA kernel optimization
				<br />
				(2) Inter-GPU communication (e.g., distributed inference serving)
			</li>
		</ul>
		<h2>Honors and Awards</h2>
		<ul class="list-inside list-disc" role="list">
			<li>
				DAC Young Fellowship, 62nd Design Automation Conference (DAC)
				(Jun. 2025)
			</li>
			<li>
				UT Excellence Engineering Fellowship, UT Austin
				(Sep. 2024)
			</li>
			<li>
				Golden Tiger Award, USAG Humphreys
				(Dec. 2019)
			</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
	.about-copy p + p {
		margin-top: -1rem;
	}
</style>
